[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    220[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - The sample cluster output (Conservative/Efficient, Thorough/Resource-Intensive, Referral-Oriented, Balanced/Guideline-Adherent) demonstrates clinically meaningful labels
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    221[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - The performance benchmarks are realistic: silhouette 0.25-0.45 for provider data, 70-80% quarter-over-quarter stability, R-squared 0.3-0.5 for case-mix models
